<h2 id="description">Description</h2>
<p>Nightmare is a 3rd person shooter game about a teddy bear that needs to save himself and a child from these nightmares during the night. If he’s lucky enough to survive the night, the teddy can be upgraded to help him with the next one.</p>

<h2 id="development">Development</h2>
<p>The game was created using Unity/C#. 2D assets were drawn using Krita software.</p>

